    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras/bcc71e72987a357d462e6b850fa454bc.avif?t=1751278775\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras_big/bcc71e72987a357d462e6b850fa454bc.avif?t=1751278775 width=800 height=891 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras/12a047888eaebbdf2792cf7ad7dce822.avif?t=1751278775\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras_big/12a047888eaebbdf2792cf7ad7dce822.avif?t=1751278775 width=800 height=1081 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras/ec352d8be8912f2883174ab5b3db1a8c.avif?t=1751278775\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras_big/ec352d8be8912f2883174ab5b3db1a8c.avif?t=1751278775 width=800 height=740 /></span><br><br><br><br><strong>Boss Fights That Hit Hard</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face four formidable zone bosses to free corrupted elemental spirits—and yes, spoiler alert—an epic final showdown awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each zone also hides minibosses, some cooler (and tougher) than the actual bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras/16f9b236171df225e5225a62d6467d57.avif?t=1751278775\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383180/extras_big/16f9b236171df225e5225a62d6467d57.avif?t=1751278775 width=800 height=611 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Combat That Keeps You Moving</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle hordes of unique enemies across every zone—each with distinct attacks, behaviors, and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain combos, unleash upgraded skills, and adapt your tactics to counter everything from agile rogues and armored brutes to chaotic wizards.<br><br><br><strong>Crafting That Matters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Love crafting? So do we. Gather resources from enemies, hidden chests, and quests to forge powerful gear and potions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your playstyle with crafted weapons, armor, and accessories. Discover builds that turn the tide of battle.<br><br><br><br></p>",
